channel.description: Well, I noticed every time I use mopar on a diffrent computer, it requires something to download, and it takes a long time. And since I have dial up at my house, it takes 2 minutes to get 1% and after 5%, the window exited itself. So, I was wondering if it was possable to download that file a diffrent way (like get that link and download it manually) So I could download it at my public library and install it at my house. And If its possable, could someone provide me a way to install it the right way so I wont mess up anything.
